@META
dir: .
updated: 2026-03-18
files: 38
stack: Next.js 14, React 18, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, Prisma 7, Tailwind CSS, NextAuth.js, Zustand, TanStack Query, Three.js, Zod, Upstash Redis, Sentry, Playwright, Jest, Storybook, Docker, Kubernetes, Helm, ArgoCD

@EXPORTS
package.json: config — npm scripts & dependencies
Dockerfile: config — multi-stage Docker build
docker-compose.yml: config — local dev stack (app + postgres)
Makefile: config — build/push/deploy shortcuts for K8s
next.config.js: config — Next.js configuration
tailwind.config.js: config — Tailwind CSS theme & plugins
tsconfig.json: config — TypeScript strict mode + path aliases (@/*)
playwright.config.ts: config — E2E test configuration
jest.config.mjs: config — unit test configuration
prisma.config.ts: config — Prisma 7 adapter config

@VARS_CONSTANTS
DATABASE_URL: string = env — PostgreSQL connection string (required)
NEXTAUTH_SECRET: string = env — session encryption key (required)
NEXTAUTH_URL: string = env — app base URL (required)
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL: string = env — rate limiting Redis (optional)
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN: string = env — Redis auth (optional)
SENTRY_DSN: string = env — error tracking (optional)

@PROCESSES
Dev: `npm run dev` → Next.js dev server on :3000
Build: `npm run build` → production Next.js build
Test: `npm test` → Jest unit tests | `npm run test:e2e` → Playwright
Lint: `npm run lint` + `npm run format:check` + `npm run type-check`
DB: `npx prisma migrate dev` → run migrations | `npx prisma studio` → GUI
Deploy: `make build` → Docker → `make push` → Harbor → ArgoCD auto-deploy
Seed: `npm run db:seed` → seed chapters & questions into PostgreSQL

@DEPENDENCIES
internal: src/, prisma/, e2e/, scripts/, data/, public/, helm/, argocd/
external: next@14, react@18, prisma@7, next-auth@4, zustand@4, @tanstack/react-query@5, zod@4, three@0.181, framer-motion@11, @upstash/redis, @sentry/nextjs@10, d3@7, bcryptjs, lucide-react, react-markdown, react-hot-toast, html2canvas, jspdf, matter-js, clsx, tailwind-merge

@STANDARDS
- App Router (not Pages Router)
- TypeScript strict mode with noUncheckedIndexedAccess
- Tailwind CSS for styling, glass morphism design system
- Zod for all API validation
- NextAuth JWT strategy for auth
- Prisma 7 with pg adapter (not Prisma default driver)
- Path alias: @/* → src/*
- ESLint + Prettier + Husky pre-commit hooks
- Czech UI text, English code/comments

@WARNINGS
- Prisma 7 uses pg adapter — NOT standard Prisma driver
- Rate limiting requires Upstash Redis — gracefully disabled without it
- 40 chapters of AI education content — static data in src/data/
- old_deprecated/ contains legacy code — do not use
- sentry configs (client/server/edge) at root level
